  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You become more difficult to move or pass, an elusive peak your enemies cannot surmount.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Wis 15, Combat Reflexes, Improved Unarmed Strike, Indomitable Mountain Style, base attack bonus +6.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Whenever an opponent succeeds at a combat maneuver against you or at an Acrobatics check to avoid provoking an attack of opportunity when moving through a square you threaten, you immediately gain a +2 morale bonus to your CMD against the next combat maneuver against you or to the DC of the next Acrobatics check to avoid an attack of opportunity when moving through a square you threaten. This bonus stacks until either attempt fails against you.",
